00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:56.900
So it's 625.

00:03:56.900 --> 00:04:02.060
So 625 is equal to AB squared.

00:04:02.060 --> 00:04:03.720
So AB is going to equal 25.

00:04:08.500 --> 00:04:11.300
So this distance, the distance
of this big hypotenuse here,

00:04:11.300 --> 00:04:12.400
