00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:22.200
But triangle BMC
right over here--

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:24.830
we know this side is 25/2.

00:08:24.830 --> 00:08:27.890
We know this side
over here is 25/2.

00:08:27.890 --> 00:08:30.760
We know this side
over here is 24.

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:33.470
And so what we want
to do is figure out

00:08:33.470 --> 00:08:36.440
the sine of this angle right
