00:08:41.850 --> 00:08:44.630
of cosines of theta plus 90.

00:08:44.630 --> 00:08:47.350
So let me redraw our triangle.

00:08:47.350 --> 00:08:52.000
So triangle BCM I
could redraw like this.

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.450
It's actually an
isosceles triangle.

00:08:54.450 --> 00:08:55.535
So we have BCM.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:00.780
And what is this
